criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. underwent coronary angiography;

          2. can complete sleep factors questionnaire.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. mental diseases;

          2. sleep apnea;

          3. chronic obstructive pulmonary disease;

          4. stroke sequelae;

          5. arthritis;

          6. renal failure;

          7. tumor and a history of revascularization.
